OL,3,CFour arrested in early hours raids
OL,4,Cover attack on woman
OL,6,FPolice investigating the attempted
OL,7,Fmurder of a woman in Huddersfield have
OL,8,Farrested four more people following a
OL,9,Fseries of early hours raids.
OL,11,FThe 30-year-old victim was left in a
OL,12,Fcritical condition after being stabbed
OL,13,Fin the head and neck on Topaz Close,
OL,14,FHuddersfield, at about 10.30pm on
OL,15,FMonday 11 May.
OL,17,FWest Yorkshire Police said officers
OL,18,Fexecuted five warrants at homes in the
OL,19,Ftown in the early hours of Thursday,
OL,20,F28 May.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
