OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780153874
OL,3,CFour arrested in early hours raids
OL,4,Cover attack on woman
OL,6,FA 35-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder. Two
OL,8,Fmen, aged 33 and 35, were arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to murder.
OL,11,FA 38-year-old woman was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,14,FTwo 17-year-old boys arrested earlier
OL,15,Fthis month on suspicion of attempted
OL,16,Fmurder remain on bail.
OL,18,FThe woman remains in hospital and
OL,19,Fpolice are continuing to appeal for
OL,20,Fwitnesses to come forward.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
